  m_Text: "\U0001F4CB Information We Collect\nWe may collect the following types
    of information:\nPersonal Information: Name, email address, and contact details
    when you sign up or contact us.\nUsage Data: Pages visited, time spent, and interactions
    within the app or website.\nDevice Information: Browser type, operating system,
    IP address, and device identifiers.\nCookies & Tracking: We use cookies to enhance
    user experience and analyze traffic.\n\U0001F6E0\uFE0F How We Use Your Information\nWe
    use your data to:\nProvide and improve our services\nPersonalize your experience\nCommunicate
    updates, offers, or support\nAnalyze usage trends and optimize performance\nEnsure
    security and prevent fraud\n\U0001F504 Sharing & Disclosure\nWe do not sell your
    personal data. We may share information with:\nService Providers: For hosting,
    analytics, and customer support\nLegal Authorities: If required by law or to
    protect our rights\nBusiness Transfers: In case of merger, acquisition, or asset
    sale\n\U0001F512 Data Security\nWe implement industry-standard security measures
    to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is
    100% secure.\n\U0001F30D International Users\nIf you're accessing our services
    from outside [Your Country], your data may be transferred and processed in [Your
    Country] where data protection laws may differ.\n\U0001F476 Children's Privacy\nOur
    services are not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect
    data from minors.\n\u2699\uFE0F Your Choices\nYou can:\nAccess, update, or delete
    your personal data\nOpt out of marketing communications\nDisable cookies via
    browser settings"
